    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for a functional daily driver. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car does show its age with some noticeable paint fading on the hood and minor scuffs around the bumpers. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few small stains, but it remains comfortable. It has been regularly serviced, though it will likely need new tires and a brake pad replacement in the near future. This is an honest, straightforward car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 19000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated restoration project or as a source for parts. The exterior displays significant wear, including deep scratches, several large dents on the rear quarter panels, and advanced rust along the wheel wells and undercarriage. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and requires immediate attention, and the transmission shifts harshly. Inside, the upholstery is heavily torn, and several electronic components, including the radio and power windows, are non-functional. Please expect to invest considerable time and resources to bring this car back to a drivable state.",
